178	       2. Parse all nested handlers within the multi item
179	       3. For each nested handler:
180	          - Use the 'match' attribute for fuzzy matching user input (or Exact Match of character code in brackets [])
181	          - Execute based on handler attributes (exec, workflow, action)
182	       4. When user input matches a handler's 'match' pattern:
